4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed to equip students with critical skills in JavaScript and Python. The program spans 18 weeks, combining 16 weeks of instructional classes plus 2 weeks for final projects, with classes held three times a week and a favorable instructor-to-student ratio of 1:7. No prior coding experience is required, and lessons are available in both English and Spanish. Participants gain hands-on experience by building applications, utilizing APIs, and completing a capstone project. Upon completion, a certification is awarded. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer). stop